column1: This file was created by CMPT_EP_CFP_OP_INV_NI_AC_RETS using the 202112 CRSP database.
It contains value- and equal-weighted returns for portfolios formed on NI.
The portfolios are constructed at the end of June. NI (net stock issues)
log of the split-adjusted shares outstanding from the fiscal year-end in t-2 to t-1.
Annual returns are from January to December.
Missing data are indicated by -99.99 or -999.
The break points include utilities and include financials.
The  portfolios  include utilities and include financials.
Value Weighted Returns -- Annual from January to December
Equal Weighted Returns -- Annual from January to December
